              <th class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-bold">Mixo</th>
              <th class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-bold">Durable</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Generation Speed</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50 font-black text-[#F59E0B]">Under 60 seconds</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">1-2 minutes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">AI Content Quality</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50">Excellent</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50">Excellent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Built-in SEO</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50">Yes</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50">Yes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">CRM/Marketing</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Basic</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50 font-black text-[#F59E0B]">Built-in CRM</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Templates</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50 font-black text-[#F59E0B]">50+ styles</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">15-20 styles</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Starting Price</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50 font-black text-[#F59E0B]">$9/mo</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">$15/mo</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Free Plan</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50">Generous</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-amber-50">Yes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Code Export</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">No</td>
              <td class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">No</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MY EXPERIENCE CASE STUDY -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-yellow-50 border-[3px] border-[#F59E0B] p-6 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MY EXPERIENCE</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>

        <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-black mb-8">
          Speed vs CRM Value: When <span class="text-[#F59E0B]">$72/Year Saves $600/Year</span>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            I tested both platforms by building a landing page for a fictional consulting business. Same prompt, same requirements, measured everything.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#F59E0B] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">THE MIXO TEST</h3>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Generated in:</strong> 47 seconds</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">First impression:</strong> Clean layout, good copy, professional design</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Edits needed:</strong> 5 minutes of customization</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900"><strong class="text-[#F59E0B]">Total to launch-ready:</strong> 6 minutes</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#F59E0B] p-6 my-6">
