            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900"><strong class="text-[#F59E0B]">Total to launch-ready:</strong> 10 minutes</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-100 border-l-[4px] border-[#F59E0B] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">THE DIFFERENCE</h3>
